{"tid":1313107,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【選舉投票制度】","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:24:09.000Z","uid":269364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"854aa447446ccb9e7cbf097a4246db6a5e8a9f41","tid":1313107,"uid":269364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成倡港府應重啟政改，給香港人普選的希望。<br />\n<br />\n假若中共點頭讓港府通過普選，也會集中票源到單一建制候選人；泛民得不到共識，多個候選人出來參選，最終因分薄票源，建制候選人高票當選。<br />\n<br />\n在此呼籲各位巴絲，思考和跟身邊人探討，我們希望用哪種方法投票？<br />\n<br />\n以下為Wiki中英文，各種選舉制度的資料，以供簡單參考：<br />\n<br />\n英文版➡️ <a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electoral_system\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FElectoral_system&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL3%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=fd16a36d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electoral_system</a><br />\n<br />\n中文版➡️ <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/投票制度\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL3%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=96744f35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/投票制度</a>"}]}